name: The Big Bad Wolf
description:
So I spent a good hot minute on this one. And I will say this is the best wolf I’ve created to date. If you’ve been following me lately. You’d know I’m experimenting. And I am very pleased with my results. Now I use to paint watercolor sceneries all the time. So it’s wild to do it again and now utilize it with my current work. Like the background wasn’t even sketched. I just painted it on the fly after the wolf.
